title: Buna brewery opening 'Texas Big' outdoor bar
text:
Published By: Beaumont Enterprise: Communities - Today 
Texas Big Beer Brewery in Buna is building an on-site bar where folks will be able to sit outside and savor Southeast Texas craft beers.
